title: Splash Pro EX 1.13.0 (& Portable) - elias1986
description:
Splash Pro EX 1.13.0 (& Portable)  by elias1986 - Pre - Activated!

DESCRIPTION:

Splash PRO - Optimized for video playback in high resolution (High Definition AVC/H.264), and view digital TV channels (DVB-T). Splash Player has a built-in codec Mirillis AVC/H.264, which is a proprietary company, and is able to provide high-quality clear and smooth images in high resolution. The player boasts a stylish, user-friendly interface.

Features:
* Supported files: AVI, MKV, MOV, M2TS, MTS, M2T, MP4, MPG, TS
* Support for video, with its own codecs: H.264, MPEG-2, VC-1
* Support video via external codecs: DivX / XviD
* The best video quality, thanks to software and hardware video decoding
* Stylish user interface and easy to use
* Supports hardware accelerated video decoding
* 1080i to 1080p conversion
* Support for multi-core processors
* Subtitles
* Lipsync amendment
* DVB-T.
